nodes.text: A Gank pulled a vibroknife on the prone form of the Sullustan journalist Den Dhur after the Gank's partner, another member of the Gank species, backhanded the Sullustan on the streets of the city–planet of Coruscant after Dhur accidentally bumped into them while drunk. When the droid I-5YQ came to Dhur's aid, the Ganks fled the scene.
